          <article><div class="top-history" id="top-about">
<div class="top-wrapper">
<h2 class="eyebrow">Our History</h2>

<p>For over four decades, we have worked to ensure that what is taught in science classrooms and beyond is accurate and consistent with the best current understanding of the scientific community.</p>
</div>
</div>
</article>
    
</div>
  </div>
